race.name: O'Reilly Auto Parts 500
race.comments: Denny Hamlin won the 23rd Annual O'Reilly Auto Parts 500 at Texas Motor Speedway, his 33rd victory in the Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series. Prior to the start of the race, the following car(s) dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reasons indicated: No. 8 (back up car) and No. 6 (multiple (2) pre-race inspection failures).
